title: Police asking for tips on arson fire during attempted break-in at Oregon Right to Life building in Keizer - Statesman Journal
content: Police asking for tips on arson fire during attempted break-in at Oregon Right to Life building in Keizer  Statesman JournalView Full Coverage on Google News
description: Arson investigators are seeking information about a fire that ignited Sunday night at the Oregon Right to Life office in Keizer after two Molotov cocktails were thrown at the building.
